data.description:
This 3-—to 4-bedroom, 2-full bath bi-level home is just what you've been looking for! It has a 2-car attached garage that leads to the laundry room. The yard has raised garden beds and mature pine trees. This home was Built in 2002. Updates include:
A new well pump (2020).
A new water heater (2022).
A new garage door (2023).
An outdoor shed with a loft (2020).
It is close to the city of Coldwater, Quincy, and Indiana.
